36:55.600 --> 36:58.353
Anything else of yours I want,
I'll let you know.

36:59.920 --> 37:01.990
- It was great.
- Thank you so much.

37:03.560 --> 37:04.993
- Night, dear.
- Okay.

37:05.200 --> 37:06.394
Peyton,

37:07.560 --> 37:09.676
I just want to say thank you
for not picking Nathan.

37:09.760 --> 37:11.432
It wasn't me. It was you.

37:11.520 --> 37:14.512
It's about time
you started to fight for your husband.

